OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781880485
OL,3,CEastenders star charged over plot to
OL,4,Csmuggle 320kg of meth into Australia
OL,6,FBritish actress Emaa Hussen has been
OL,7,Fcharged after allegedly trying to
OL,8,Fsmuggle 320kg of methamphetamine into
OL,9,FAustralia from West Africa.
OL,11,FThe 34-year-old, who is best known for
OL,12,Fplaying Naz in Eastenders spin-off E20
OL,13,Fand also appeared in Jason Statham's
OL,14,Faction-thriller 'Hummingbird',
OL,15,Fappeared in a Sydney court on Thursday.
OL,17,FPolice allege Hussen, along with a
OL,18,Fcouple from South Australia, tried to
OL,19,Fimport methamphetamine by hiding it in
OL,20,Fbags of charcoal in shipping
OL,21,Fcontainers from Ghana.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
