PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781880485
OL,3,CEastenders star charged over plot to
OL,4,Csmuggle 320kg of meth into Australia
OL,6,FPolice launched an investigation after
OL,7,FAustralian Border Force officers
OL,8,Fdetected 'anomalies' in the containers.
OL,10,FOfficers x-rayed the bags and found a
OL,11,Fwhite crystalised substance which
OL,12,Freturned a positive result for
OL,13,Fmethamphetamine.
OL,15,FThe bags contained around 320kg of the
OL,16,Fdrug which has an estimated street
OL,17,Fvalue of $296 million AUD (about
OL,18,F#157m).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781880485
OL,3,CEastenders star charged over plot to
OL,4,Csmuggle 320kg of meth into Australia
OL,6,FThe drugs were removed from the
OL,7,Fshipment by police before it was
OL,8,Fdelivered to a storage facility in
OL,9,FSydney's western suburbs.
OL,11,FPolice allege that Hussen went to the
OL,12,Fstorage facility and supervised a
OL,13,Fnumber of men as they unpacked the
OL,14,Fcontainer.
OL,16,FSeveral bags were then loaded into a
OL,17,Fvehicle and driven to a house nearby
OL,18,Fin Blacktown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781880485
OL,3,CEastenders star charged over plot to
OL,4,Csmuggle 320kg of meth into Australia
OL,6,FShortly afterwards, officers
OL,7,Finvestigators executed a search
OL,8,Fwarrant at the house, where Hussen was
OL,9,Farrested.
OL,11,FPolice found 32 bags inside, which
OL,12,Fwere allegedly those that had
OL,13,Fpreviously contained methamphetamine.
OL,15,FOfficers also seized electronic
OL,16,Fdevices and a notebook.
OL,18,FA woman, 30 and a man, 32 were
OL,19,Farrested in Adelaide for allegedly
OL,20,Fattempting to rent the storage units
OL,21,Fin Sydney by using false identities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
