OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781880485
OL,3,CEastenders star charged over plot to
OL,4,Csmuggle 320kg of meth into Australia
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FDetective Acting Superintendent Trevor
OL,12,FRobinson said the Australian Federal
OL,13,FPolice is continuing to investigate
OL,14,Fthe suppliers and key facilitators of
OL,15,Fthe drug importation.
OL,17,FHussen's charge of attempting to
OL,18,Fimport a commercial quantity of
OL,19,Fmethamphetamine into Australia carries
OL,20,Fa maximum penalty of life in prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
